text = "Here you will design the circuity needed to build your toy. In this
day and age, even the most basic toys requires some digital circuitry.

Connect the START chip to the END chip by rotating the GREEN chips.
RED chips cannot be rotated. The electrical signal only travels so far
so be sure to use REPEATER chips (the ones with thick yellow lines)
to boost the strength of your current."
